{"tid":2062532,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"傳聘韓國瑜當北市副市長？柯P回應了","createTime":"2020-06-13T07:57:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T17:16:36.000Z","uid":54870,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"40a8bb8a04c2116c7e9286f69e92e4231428a065","tid":2062532,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T07:57:39.000Z","msg":"高雄市長韓國瑜12日下午正式被中選會公告解除市長職位，台北市長柯文哲下午前往台北市議會進行市政總質詢，民進黨台北市議員王世堅質詢問到，外界傳出「你要聘任韓國瑜當台北市副市長？」柯文哲打趣的說，「這樣講3個副市長要被你嚇死了。」<br />\n<br />\n下午3時左右也正值韓國瑜被解職，王世堅也問到怎麼看傳韓國瑜要聘為台北市副市長？柯文哲笑回，這樣講3個副市長都要嚇死了，這是假訊息吧，假訊息至少也要三分真。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%82%B3%E8%81%98%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E7%91%9C%E7%95%B6%E5%8C%97%E5%B8%82%E5%89%AF%E5%B8%82%E9%95%B7-%E6%9F%AFp%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E4%BA%86-080509080.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%2582%25B3%25E8%2581%2598%25E9%259F%2593%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2591%259C%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%258C%2597%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%2589%25AF%25E5%25B8%2582%25E9%2595%25B7-%25E6%259F%25AFp%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589%25E4%25BA%2586-080509080.html&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrtg1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=d75f487c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%82%B3%E8%81%98%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E7%91%9C%E7%95%B6%E5%8C%97%E5%B8%82%E5%89%AF%E5%B8%82%E9%95%B7-%E6%9F%AFp%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E4%BA%86-080509080.html</a>"},{"pid":"8eecedc80803273917876a42d834fb0c8143bb1b","tid":2062532,"uid":17641,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T07:59:41.000Z","msg":"2022年香港特首=韓國瑜，政務司=譚德塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"453ca69c477eddeeafa4b2b566166f71ec3eee37","tid":2062532,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8eecedc80803273917876a42d834fb0c8143bb1b","tid":2062532,"uid":17641,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T07:59:41.000Z","msg":"2022年香港特首=韓國瑜，政務司=譚德塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj